+# Gatekeeper
+
+Review Flatpak manifests.
+
+## Overview
+
+🚧 This project is a work-in-progress! Instructions will be added as soon as it is usable. 🚧
+
+## Contributing
+
+To contribute, please use the [Codeberg flow](https://docs.codeberg.org/collaborating/) and follow the [GNOME Code of Conduct](https://conduct.gnome.org/).
+
+To build and start a development version of Gatekeeper locally, run the following:
+
+```shell
+$ git clone https://codeberg.org/pojntfx/gatekeeper
+$ cd gatekeeper
+$ go generate ./...
+$ go run -ldflags="-X 'main.LocaleDir=${PWD}/po' -X 'main.SchemaDir=${PWD}/assets/resources'" .
+```
+
